EASTERN CARIBBEAN SEA.
SAINT LUCIA.
DNC 14.
1. KAYAK, BLUE AND BLACK HULL, ONE PERSON ONBOARD,
   OVERDUE CASTRIES (14-01N 060-59W) TO 14-27N 061-49W
   AND RETURN. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO
   KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO MRCC FORT DE FRANCE,
   INMARSAT-C: 422799024, TELEX: 42912008,
   PHONE: 5965 9670 9292, FAX: 5965 9663 2450,
   E-MAIL: ANTILLES@MRCCFR.EU.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1535/17.
